snippet.textDisplay: I missed seeing the episode live and heard that they had a go at Ustad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan's Afreen Afreen... and I was like NO! You don't mess with that brilliance and then I came online literally with my heart pounding... and VOILA! They could not have done it better than this! I wouldn't say it's an improvement on the original song but if this isn't the best tribute to the great USTAD, nothing is! And Momina Mustehsin, kya baat hai! I have loved her voice since Awari (Ek Villain) but she has proved that she has a lot more class than we thought.
